definitions.definition: Approaching or about to take place .
examples: I shall vote in the forthcoming election.

definitions.definition: Available when needed ; in place , ready .
Willing to co-operate or provide information ; candid , frank , responsive .
examples: Once I explained why I needed to know, she was really forthcoming .
